title: Per Capita Personal Consumption Expenditures: Services: Final Consumption Expenditures of Nonprofit Institutions Serving Households: Gross Output of Nonprofit Institutions for New Jersey
notes:
Personal consumption expenditures of a given area divided by the resident population of the area.

Gross output is net of unrelated sales, secondary sales, and sales to business, government, and the rest of the world; excludes own-account investment (construction and software).For more information about this release go to http://www.bea.gov/newsreleases/regional/pce/pce_newsrelease.htm.
